G1 Z10 F1000;        ; Raise brush
G0 X5 Y5 F1200;     ; Rapid move to clean
G1 Z-1 F800;         ; Lower brush
G1 X10 Y12 Z8 F1200;     ; Move
G1 Z-1 F800;         ; Lower
